"and antibiotic days are recorded in the chart, if possible on a daily "
"basis.  This chart must be kept at your facility and to simplify data "
"collection and patient follow-up.  You must maintain patient progress "
"chart(s) for every eligible infant during the surveillance period.  It is "
"possible to enter up to six different antibiotic substances in one chart.  "
