"CVC\" / \"Total CVC Days\" xx 1000]"
msgstr ""
"stem:[\"ZVK-associated BSI Rate\" = \"Total BSI Cases in Patients With "
"ZVK\" / \"Total ZVK Days\" xx 1000]"

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/protocol/NeoIPC-Core-Protocol.adoc:893
